@startuml
title Scrum 工件关系图

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

package "Scrum 工件" {
    component [产品待办事项列表\nProduct Backlog] as pbl #lightgreen
    component [Sprint 待办事项列表\nSprint Backlog] as sbl #lightyellow
    component [产品增量\nIncrement] as increment #lightblue
}

package "Product Backlog 属性" {
    component [待办事项项\n(用户故事、功能、缺陷)] as pbi
    component [优先级\n(由产品负责人决定)] as priority
    component [估算\n(故事点、理想小时)] as estimate
    component [验收标准] as criteria
}

package "Sprint Backlog 属性" {
    component [Sprint 目标] as goal
    component [选定的待办事项项] as selected
    component [任务分解] as tasks
    component [每日进度更新] as progress
}

package "增量属性" {
    component [完成的功能] as features
    component [质量标准\n(完成定义)] as quality
    component [可发布状态] as releasable
}

' Product Backlog 组成部分
pbl --> pbi
pbl --> priority
pbl --> estimate
pbl --> criteria

' Sprint Backlog 组成部分
sbl --> goal
sbl --> selected
sbl --> tasks
sbl --> progress

' 增量组成部分
increment --> features
increment --> quality
increment --> releasable

' 工件之间的关系
pbl --> sbl : 选择项目创建
sbl --> increment : 完成交付
increment ..> pbl : 可能产生新需求

note right of pbl
  产品待办事项列表
  - 动态更新
  - 持续细化
  - 按优先级排序
  - 包含所有产品需求
end note

note right of sbl
  Sprint 待办事项列表
  - Sprint 期间的计划
  - 由开发团队拥有
  - 每日更新
  - 可见和透明
end note

note right of increment
  产品增量
  - 可工作的产品功能
  - 符合完成定义
  - 可随时发布
  - 累积所有之前的增量
end note

@enduml

